{"word":"H7965 - שָׁלֹום - shâlôwm - shaw-lome' - [idiom] do","slug":"H7965","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁלֹום</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâlôwm"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-lome'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>[idiom] do"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁלם שׁלום</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>shâlôm shâlôm</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>shaw-lome'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p><ol><li>completeness, soundness, welfare, peace<ol type='a'><li>completeness (in number)</li><li>safety, soundness (in body)</li><li>welfare, health, prosperity</li><li>peace, quiet, tranquillity, contentment</li><li>peace, friendship<ol><li>of human relationships</li><li>with God especially in covenant relationship</li></ol><li>peace (from war)</li><li>peace (as adjective)</li></ol></li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7999\">H7999</a> <p />TWOT entry: <a class=\"T\" href=\"S:2401 - shalem\">2401a</a> <p />Part(s) of speech: Noun Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3073\">H3073</a>, <a href=\"#/H4918\">H4918</a>, <a href=\"#/H4919\">H4919</a>, <a href=\"#/H4920\">H4920</a>, <a href=\"#/H4921\">H4921</a>, <a href=\"#/H4922\">H4922</a>, <a href=\"#/H7966\">H7966</a>, <a href=\"#/H7967\">H7967</a>, <a href=\"#/H7968\">H7968</a>, <a href=\"#/H7999\">H7999</a>, <a href=\"#/H8002\">H8002</a>, <a href=\"#/H8003\">H8003</a>, <a href=\"#/H8004\">H8004</a>, <a href=\"#/H8005\">H8005</a>, <a href=\"#/H8006\">H8006</a>, <a href=\"#/H8010\">H8010</a>, <a href=\"#/H8011\">H8011</a>, <a href=\"#/H8013\">H8013</a>, <a href=\"#/H8015\">H8015</a>, <a href=\"#/H8016\">H8016</a>, <a href=\"#/H8017\">H8017</a>, <a href=\"#/H8018\">H8018</a>, <a href=\"#/H8019\">H8019</a>, <a href=\"#/H8020\">H8020</a>, <a href=\"#/H8021\">H8021</a>, <a href=\"#/H8022\">H8022</a>"}]}